---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Smart AI Hacks">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 px-4">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-white text-center">About <span class="text-primary">Smart AI Hacks</span></h1>
		
		<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-left space-y-8">
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-center">
				Welcome to Smart AI Hacks, your essential resource for mastering Artificial Intelligence in your daily life. In a fast-paced world, our mission is clear: to simplify AI complexity and transform advanced tools into practical solutions for your productivity and creativity.
			</p>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Our Mission: Connecting Innovation and Usability</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300">
					We believe AI shouldn't be a mystery. Smart AI Hacks was born to be the bridge between technological innovation and efficient execution. We are dedicated to exploring, testing, and filtering the best strategies so you can work smarter, not harder.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">What We Mean by "Hacks"</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300">
					At Smart AI Hacks, we use the word "hacks" to describe clever shortcuts, productivity tips, and creative techniques to solve problems. Whether it's a refined prompt for ChatGPT, a workflow automation, or a hidden feature in a new tool, our goal is to help you "hack" your learning curve and achieve extraordinary results in less time.
				</p>
				<div class="bg-darker p-4 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 rounded-r mt-4">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 m-0">
						<strong>Ethical Note:</strong> We are a strictly educational platform focused on productivity and technology. We do not support, encourage, or provide information on illegal activities or software piracy.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">What You Will Find Here</h2>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Prompt Engineering</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Learn how to interact with language models to get the best results.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Tool Reviews</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Honest, technical reviews of the latest AI software.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Workflows</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Step-by-step guides to integrating AI into your business or studies.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Tech News</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Stay updated with the dynamic world of Artificial Intelligence.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300">
					We are a team of tech enthusiasts and AI explorers passionate about the future of work. We personally test everything we write about to ensure you receive accurate, safe, and practical advice.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="bg-darker p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary/20">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">AI Disclaimer</h2>
				<div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
					<p>The information provided on Smart AI Hacks (https://smartaihacks.tech) is strictly for educational and entertainment purposes.</p>
					<p><strong>AI Accuracy:</strong> Artificial Intelligence is a constantly evolving technology. While we test all prompts and tools, AI models can generate inaccurate or inconsistent responses.</p>
					<p><strong>User Responsibility:</strong> The use of any "hack", automation, or command suggested on this site is the sole responsibility of the user. We are not responsible for data loss, system errors, or financial/professional decisions made based on AI-generated content.</p>
					<p><strong>No Guarantees:</strong> We do not guarantee that results obtained today with a tool will be the same tomorrow, due to constant updates from developers (OpenAI, Google, Anthropic, etc).</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<div class="text-center mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
				<p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Thank you for visiting, and letâ€™s unlock the limitless potential of AI together!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
